@startuml
title Devils Resting - Chat Session State
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor #ffffff
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam nodesep 45
skinparam ranksep 55
skinparam roundcorner 10
skinparam ArrowColor #687385
skinparam ArrowThickness 1.1
skinparam state {
  BorderColor #9fb0c7
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  FontColor #1f2937
}
skinparam note {
  BorderColor #d7dee8
  BackgroundColor #fbfcfe
  FontColor #445066
}

[*] --> Idle

Idle --> ResolveTarget : navigate to /:target
ResolveTarget : POST /api/chat/resolve/
ResolveTarget --> AccessDenied : 400 / 401 / 403 / 404
ResolveTarget --> LoadRoom : roomId resolved

LoadRoom : GET room details + messages
LoadRoom --> PassiveView : guest public room
LoadRoom --> ConnectRealtime : authenticated room\nor ws-enabled route

PassiveView --> ConnectRealtime : session becomes available
PassiveView --> [*] : navigate away

ConnectRealtime : build /ws/chat/<roomId>/
ConnectRealtime --> Active : socket open
ConnectRealtime --> Reconnecting : error / close before ready

state Active {
  [*] --> Synced

  Synced --> Typing : send typing event
  Typing --> Synced : timeout or message sent

  Synced --> Uploading : queue attachments
  Uploading --> Synced : uploads complete
  Uploading --> ComposerError : upload failed or canceled
  ComposerError --> Synced : retry or clear queue

  Synced --> ReadSync : mark_read
  ReadSync --> Synced : read ack received

  Synced --> RateLimited : slow mode or 429
  RateLimited --> Synced : retry_after elapsed
}

Active --> Reconnecting : socket closed / browser offline
Reconnecting --> ConnectRealtime : backoff retry
Reconnecting --> Degraded : retry limit reached
Degraded --> ConnectRealtime : manual reconnect\nor network restored

Active --> MembershipRevoked : kicked / banned /\npermission revoked
AccessDenied --> [*]
MembershipRevoked --> [*]
Active --> [*] : navigate away / logout
Degraded --> [*] : leave page

note right of Active
The same reconnecting websocket primitive
is reused by presence and direct inbox providers.
end note
@enduml
